  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/08/google-camera-photos-in-mid-recording/\"><img alt=\"Google Camera app for Android\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/73b95b9519720f5766bee6673fa5b327/200038743/googlecamera.jpg\" style=\"height: 335px; width: 620px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n虽说在<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/16/google-stock-camera-app-photo-sphere-lens-blur/\">之前的更新</a>中 Google 为自己的 Android 相机应用加入了重新对焦、浅景深等有趣功能，但它有一个问题是，在录影的过程中不能拍照了。对部分用户来说这是不可缺少的，而现在 Google 显然也意识到了这一点。在今日上线的更新中他们悄悄加回了这项功能，让用户在留住那些美好过程的同时，也能定格下想要珍藏的画面。如果你有这方面需要的话，那不要犹豫赶快升级吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/05/08/google-camera-photos-in-mid-recording/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.phonearena.com/news/Google-Camera-gets-back-the-ability-to-capture-snapshots-while-recording-videos_id55925\" target=\"_blank\">Phone Arena</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.GoogleCamera&amp;hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Google Play</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/08/google-camera-photos-in-mid-recording/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20882755/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/08/google-camera-photos-in-mid-recording/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
